<div class="backing-2">
  <h2>Sponsorships</h2>
  <p>Since opening in August 2017, we have had <%=@members.count()%> members make a total of <%=@sponsorships.count()%> pledges.</p>
  <p>At present we are lucky enough to be collecting Â£<%=Sponsorship.total_value%> /month to support our animal advocates in their endeavours<br>
  You too can add your name to those below by simply joining the Red Centre Conservation Society and making a pledge below.</p>
<div>
  <p><a class="button" href="/members/new">Join now</a></p>
  <p><a class="button" href="/sponsorships/new">Make a pledge today!</a></p>
<!--flex, flex grow?, remove width restriction. -->
    <div class="form-container">
    <% for record in @sponsorships do %>
      <div class="form-pledge">
        <div class="profile-pic ani-pic" style="background-image: url('<%=record.sponsor.picture%>')"></div>
          <div class="pledge-text">
            <p>Pledge number:<%=record.id%></p>
            <p><a href="/members/<%=record.member_id%>"><%=record.sponsor.name.capitalize%></a> is currently sponsoring <a href="/animals/<%=record.animal_id%>"><%=record.sponsored.name.capitalize%></a></p>
            <p><a href="/sponsorships/<%=record.id%>">Click for more details</a></p>
          </div>
        <div class="profile-pic ani-pic" style="background-image: url('<%=record.sponsored.image%>')"></div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
